<emphasis box="[463,676,404,428]" italics="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="20">Acanthobatesianus</emphasis>
is a combination of parts of the names 
<taxonomicName box="[1117,1269,404,428]" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" genus="Acanthocinus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="19" pageNumber="20" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
